---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About — alexajuno" description="A bit about Giao — developer, builder, blogger.">
  <section class="pb-8 pt-8 sm:pb-20 sm:pt-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">About</h1>
  </section>

  <div class="prose prose-zinc max-w-none dark:prose-invert prose-headings:font-semibold prose-a:text-accent-600 prose-a:no-underline hover:prose-a:underline dark:prose-a:text-accent-400">
    <!-- Intro — feel free to rewrite this in your own words -->
    <p>
      Hi, I'm Giao, a developer. Nice to meet you.
    </p>
    <p>
      I'm less than a year into this, figuring things out one project at a time.
      I like building real things and writing about the process honestly. Not
      polished tutorials, just what actually happened.
    </p>

    <!-- What I'm working on — replace with your current projects/interests -->
    <h2>What I'm working on</h2>
    <p>
      Right now I'm focused on learning by doing. Building projects, breaking
      things, reading docs, and writing about all of it on this blog. If
      something I went through helps someone else, that's a bonus.
    </p>

    <!-- Get in touch -->
    <h2>Get in touch</h2>
    <p>
      I'm always happy to connect. You can find me here:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <a href="https://github.com/alexajuno" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="mailto:giolynx104@gmail.com">giolynx104@gmail.com</a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
